# Monorepo Commands

## Backend (Java/Vert.x)

```bash
cd backend/server && mvn clean install        # build + test
cd backend/server && mvn verify               # tests + checkstyle
```

## Frontend (React/TypeScript)

```bash
cd pulse-ui && yarn install && yarn start     # dev server on :3000
cd pulse-ui && yarn build                     # production build
cd pulse-ui && yarn lint                      # ESLint
```

## AI Agent (Python/FastAPI)

```bash
cd pulse_ai && pip install -r requirements.txt
cd pulse_ai && ./scripts/run_api.sh           # uvicorn on :8001
```

## Docker (full stack)

```bash
cd deploy && ./scripts/quickstart.sh          # build + start all
cd deploy && ./scripts/build.sh [ui|server|ai|all]
cd deploy && ./scripts/start.sh -d [ui|server|ai]
cd deploy && ./scripts/stop.sh [-v]
cd deploy && ./scripts/logs.sh [service]
```

## Key Ports

| Service | Port | Health |
|---------|------|--------|
| pulse-server | 8080 | `/healthcheck` |
| pulse-ui | 3000 | `/healthcheck.txt` |
| pulse-ai | 8001 | `/list-apps` |
| alerts-cron | 4000 | `/healthcheck` |
| ClickHouse | 8123 (HTTP), 9000 (native) | `SELECT 1` |
| MySQL | 3307 | `mysqladmin ping` |
| Kafka UI | 8081 | — |
| OTEL Collector 1 | 4317/4318, 13133 (health) | — |

